      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. GOT A SYSTEM shapes well after a solid run last time, finishing second in a Maiden at this track in 18.38. Expected to push the clock again here. 1. ONLY RUMOURS is a Garry Small-trained newcomer by Fernando Bale out of Armatree Kaycee with no trial form to work with. Gets her chance from the draw. Profiles well but prefer to see a move in betting. 2. SILVERTREE ADAM clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 3 length second behind Oat Latte in 18.93. Bold showing expected again. 3. ANOTHER RUSSIAN has claims fresh from a recent placing.\",\"runners\":[7,1,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
